  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
    @Embeddable
@VoDml(id="coords:JD",
       role=dataType)
public class JD
extends TimeInstant
implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
    Extension of TimeInstant for time expressed in Julian days. Note that JD does not properly specify a time stamp unless it is related to a time scale and reference position. Precision can easily become an issue with JD, as the numbers tend to be large. dataType: JD
